== 例外 ==
2004年，研究人员合成了一种称为{{link-en|5-脱氢-1,3-醌二甲烷自由基|5-dehydro-m-xylylene|DMX}}的三[[自由基|自由基]]<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/anie.200352990|pages=742–745|title=5-Dehydro-1,3-quinodimethane: A Hydrocarbon with an Open-Shell Doublet Ground State|journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition|volume=43|issue=6|date=2004-01-30|issn=1521-3773|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1002/anie.200352990|author=Lyudmila V. Slipchenko, Tamara E. Munsch, Paul G. Wenthold, Anna I. Krylov}}</ref>，是第一个被发现不符合洪德规则的有机体系<ref>{{cite news|url=http://physicsworld.com/cws/article/news/2004/feb/11/radical-molecule-breaks-the-rules|title=Radical molecule breaks the rules|accessdate=2014-09-10|archive-date=2014-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219085915/http://physicsworld.com/cws/article/news/2004/feb/11/radical-molecule-breaks-the-rules|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

